edator-ending-almost-went-totally-off-the-rails-with-an-ellen-ripley-cameo/|title='The Predator' Ending Almost Went Totally Off the Rails with an Ellen Ripley Cameo [UPDATED]|last=Anderton|first=Ethan|date=January 2, 2019|website=/Film|accessdate=March 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! Rebecca \"Newt\" Jorden\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|}\n\n===Additional crew===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | Crew/Detail\n! colspan=\"4\" | Film\n|-\n! align=\"center\" width=\"19%\" | ''[[Predator (film)|Predator]]''\n! align=\"center\" width=\"19%\" | ''[[Predator 2]]''\n! align=\"center\" width=\"19%\" | ''[[Predators (film)|Predators]]''\n! align=\"center\" width=\"19%\" | ''[[The Predator (film)|The Predator]]''\n|-\n! 1987\n! 1990\n! 2010\n! 2018\n|-\n! Composer(s)\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Alan Silvestri]]\n| [[John Debney]]\n| [[Henry Jackman]]\n|-\n! Cinematography\n| [[Donald McAlpine]]\n| [[Peter Levy (cinematographer)|Peter Levy]]\n| [[Gyula Pados]]\n| [[Larry Fong]]\n|-\n! Editor(s)\n| [[Mark Helfrich (film editor)|Mark Helfrich]] <br />John F. Link\n| [[Mark Goldblatt]] <br/>Bert Lovitt\n| [[Dan Zimmerman]]\n| Harry B. Miller III <br/>[[Billy Weber]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Production companies\n| colspan=\"4\" | [[Davis Entertainment]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" | Lawrence Gordon Productions <br />[[Silver Pictures]]\n| [[Dune Entertainment]] <br />[[Troublemaker Studios]] <br />[[Ingenious Media]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | 20th Century Fox <br />Silver Pictures <br />Lawrence Gordon Productions <br />[[Davis Entertainment]]\n|-\n! Distributing company\n| colspan=\"4\" | [[20th Century Fox]]\n|-\n! Running time\n| 107 minutes\n| 108 minutes\n| 107 minutes\n| 107 minutes<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tiff.net/tiff/the-predator/|title=The Predator at the Toronto International Film Festival|work=tiff |date= |accessdate=August 9, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Reception==\n\n===Box office performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"