90\n| $30,669,413\n| $26,450,905\n| $57,120,318\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| #2,605\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $35 million{{Citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web | url= https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=predator2.htm | title=Predator 2 (1990) | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate= 2013-03-08 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Predators (film)|Predators]]''\n| July 9, 2010\n| $52,000,688\n| $75,232,420\n| $127,233,108\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| #1,584\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $40 million\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=predators.htm | title=Predators (2010) | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2013-03-08}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[The Predator (film)|The Predator]]''\n| September 14, 2018\n| $51,024,708\n| $109,517,426\n| $160,542,134\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| #3,051\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $88 million\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=thepredator.htm |title= The Predator (2018) |work= [[Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate= September 12, 2018 }}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|Total\n! ${{val|fmt=commas|{{#expr:59735548+30669413+52000688+24000000}}}}\n! ${{val|fmt=commas|{{#expr:38532010+26450905+75232420+30727235}}}}\n! ${{val|fmt=commas|{{#expr:98267558+57120318+127233108+54727235}}}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| N/A\n! $178 million\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| N/A\n|-\n| colspan=\"9\" | <small>'''List indicator(s)'''\n* <sup>(E)</sup> indicates figures based on available information.</small>\n<small>Please note that the figures in this table are not inflation adjusted</small>\n|}\n\n===Critical response===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:99%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! '''Film'''\n! '''[[Rotten Tomatoes]]'''\n! '''[[Metacritic]]'''\n! '''[[CinemaScore]]'''\n|-\n| ''Predator''\n| 81% (47 reviews)<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.rotte