 (director)|Ranjith]]\n*[[K. P. A. C. Lalitha|K.P.A.C Lalitha]]\n*[[Monisha Unni|Monisha]]\n*[[Revathi]]\n*[[Seema (actress)|Seema]]\n*[[Shweta Menon|Swetha Menon]]\n*[[Ambika (actress)|Ambika]]\n*[[Sukumari]]\n*[[Aranmula Ponnamma]]\n*[[Urvashi (actress)|Urvashi]]\n*[[Kalaranjini]]\n*[[Kalpana (Malayalam actress)|Kalpana]]\n*[[Vidhubala]]\n*[[M. G. Soman|M.G Soman]]\n*[[Krishna (Malayalam actor)|Krishna]]\n\n*[[Sudheesh]]\n*[[Biju Menon]]\n*[[Venu Nagavally]]\n*[[Jayabharathi]]\n* [[Sukumaran]]\n* [[Prithviraj Sukumaran]]\n* [[Indrajith Sukumaran]]\n* [[Balachandra Menon]]\n*[[Janardhanan (actor)|Janardhanan]]\n*[[Narendra Prasad]]\n*[[Bichu Thirumala|Bichu Tirumala]]\n*[[Bharathan]]\n*[[Bheeman Raghu]]\n*[[Ravi Vallathol]]\n*[[Unni Mukundan]]\n*[[Kollam Thulasi]]\n* [[Saiju Kurup]]\n* [[Jagadeesh]]\n* [[ Shobhana ]]\n*[[Bhagyalakshmi]] - Dubbing Artist\n*[[Saikumar (actor)|Saikumar]]\n*[[Shobha Mohan]]\n*[[Vinu Mohan]]\n*[[Vijayaraghavan|Vijaya Raghavan]]\n*[[N. N. Pillai|N.N.Pillai]]\n*[[Parvathy Jayaram|Parvathi Jayaram]]\n*[[Anusree]]\n*[[Keerthy Suresh|Keerthi Suresh]]\n*[[Navya Nair]]\n*[[Bhavana (actress)|Bhavana]]\n*[[Bhama]]\n*[[Anoop Menon]]\n*[[Anil Nedumangad]]\n*[[Shyamaprasad]]\n*[[G. Aravindan]]\n* [[ Thikkurissi Sukumaran Nair ]]\n* [[ Kottarakkara Sreedharan Nair ]]\n* [[ Balan K Nair ]]\n* [[ Oduvil Unnikrishnan ]]\n* [[ Shankaradi ]]\n*[[Poojappura Ravi]]\n* [[ Karamana Janardanan Nair ]]\n*[[Sudheer Karamana]]\n*[[Murali Gopy|Murali Gopi]]\n*[[Maniyanpilla Raju]]\n*  [[Vishak Nair|Vishakh Nair]]\n* [[ K K Menon ]]\n*[[Vineeth]]\n*[[Madhupal]]\n*[[K. B. Ganesh Kumar|Ganesh Kumar]]\n*[[Rajeev Pillai|Rajeev pillai]]\n*[[Murali (Malayalam actor)|Murali]]\n*[[Krishna Kumar (actor)|Krishnakumar]]\n*[[KK (singer)|KK]] Singer\n*[[M. Jayachandran|M.Jayachandran]]\n*[[Suraj Venjaramoodu]]\n* [[C. V. Raman Pillai]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rr20K3WL-qgC&pg=PA51 |title=C.V. Raman Pillai |page=51 |website=Books.google.com |date= |a