ir]] - Leela group\n*[[Rajan Pillai]] - Former CFO of Britania Group\n*[[Rajeev Chandrasekhar]] -Founder of BPL Mobile also the chairman of Jupiter Capital owned Asianet News \n*[[E. Sreedharan]] - Chairman of DMC also known as The Metro Man \n*[[Sashi Kumar]] - Founder of Asianet \n*[[Atlas Ramachandran]] - Businessman\n\n== Journalists, Cartoonists and Radio / TV News Professionals ==\n*[[Chengalathu Kunhirama Menon]]\n*[[Kutty (cartoonist)]]\n*[[K. Shankar Pillai]]\n*[[Appan Menon]]\n*[[C. Karunakara Menon]]\n\n== Arts & Literature ==\n* [[Jayan]]\n* [[Bharath Gopi]]\n* [[Madhu]]\n* [[M. N. Nambiar]]\n*[[Prathapachandran]]\n* [[Nedumudi Venu]]\n* [[Suresh Gopi]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Philip|first=Shaju|title=Kerala actor Suresh Gopi snubbed by Hindu Nair leader|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-others/kerala-actor-suresh-gopi-snubbed-by-hindu-nair-leader/|accessdate= 28 December 2016|work=[[The Indian Express]]|location=Kerala|date=27 June 2015}}</ref>\n* [[Adoor Bhasi]]\n*[[Thoppil Bhasi]]\n*[[Adoor Gopalakrishnan]]\n*[[Padmarajan]]\n*[[G. K. Pillai (actor)|G.K Pillai]]\n* [[Dileep]]\n* [[Mohanlal]]\n* [[Priyadarshan]]\n*[[Shankar (actor)|Shankar]]\n*[[Major Ravi]]\n*[[Revathy Kalamandhir|G.Suresh Kumar]]\n*[[Gautham Menon]]\n*[[Ashokan (actor)|Ashokan]]\n*[[Raghuvaran]]\n*[[Shaji Kailas]]\n*[[Renji Panicker|Renji Paniker]]\n*[[Viji Thampi]]\n*[[Vinayan]]\n*[[Rajasenan]]\n*[[Ranjith (director)|Ranjith]]\n*[[K. P. A. C. Lalitha|K.P.A.C Lalitha]]\n*[[Monisha Unni|Monisha]]\n*[[Revathi]]\n*[[Seema (actress)|Seema]]\n*[[Shweta Menon|Swetha Menon]]\n*[[Ambika (actress)|Ambika]]\n*[[Sukumari]]\n*[[Aranmula Ponnamma]]\n*[[Urvashi (actress)|Urvashi]]\n*[[Kalaranjini]]\n*[[Kalpana (Malayalam actress)|Kalpana]]\n*[[Vidhubala]]\n*[[M. G. Soman|M.G Soman]]\n*[[Krishna (Malayalam actor)|Krishna]]\n\n*[[Sudheesh]]\n*[[Biju Menon]]\n*[[Venu Nagavally]]\n*[[Jayabharathi]]\n* [[Sukumaran]]\n* [[Prithviraj Sukumaran]]\n* [[Indrajith Sukumaran]]\n* [[Balachandra Meno